---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import meImage from '../../assets/me.png';
import Heading from '../Heading/Heading.astro';
import Prose from '../Prose/Prose.astro';
import styles from './About.module.scss';
---

<main class={styles.About}>
  <Image
    src={meImage}
    width={294}
    height={294}
    alt="Ján Korkoš"
    class={styles.About__photo}
    loading="eager"
  />
  <Heading as="h1" class={styles.About__name} id="about-heading">Ján Korkoš</Heading>
  <div class={styles.About__job}>Frontend developer</div>

  <Prose tag="section">
    <p>Hi, I'm Ján. I'm a software developer focused mainly on frontend development and modern web applications.</p>
    <p>After finishing my studies I moved to Prague, where I worked at Alma Career on the product Atmoskop as a full-stack developer with a strong focus on frontend.</p>
    <p>Outside of work I enjoy learning and building things in different ways. I love swing dancing and regularly attend international festivals. I also enjoy photography, experimenting with small electronics projects using Arduino and ESP boards, and taking care of plants or growing them from seeds.</p>
  </Prose>
</main>
